data.description: Welcome Home! Eligible Veterans can assume a 2.75% mortgage! Completely maintenance free inside and out! Updates include: Solar (2023) Save an average of $4,000 a year in electric bills – Attic foam/insulation (2023), New AC units (2022), Exterior paint (2022), Interior paint (2021), New Water Softener System (2021), 7 Stage Reverse Osmosis kitchen system (2021), New High Impact weather resistant French Doors (with built in blinds) and Windows (2021). The Front covered entrance leads you into the large spaces, luxury vinyl wood look flooring throughout the home, large master bedroom with His and Hers walk in closets with built-ins, electric fireplace (2023) and large sitting area, master bathroom with walk-in tile shower with multiple jets and rain showerhead and double vanities. This split bedroom concept home has a second private bedroom and bathroom with walk in shower, two additional bedrooms with a tub and shower bathroom to share and then there is a separate office. Open concept family room and kitchen with a 9 ft. breakfast bar, Granite counters, spacious island with electricity, 5 burner gas stove top, double built in ovens, new dishwasher (2021),new microwave (2022) and beautiful solid wood cabinets. Huge walk-in pantry with automatic lighting when you enter. Wood shutters throughout the entire home. Large laundry room inside leading to the 3 car garage. . This home also features indoor-outdoor living with 3 sets of French doors leading the way to your 24 by 20 screened in paver patio with outdoor kitchen, grill (Natural Gas ), upper and lower cabinets, Granite counter and sink. Additional insulation on the garage doors and above the garage and above the lanai (2023), with conditioned space for storage. Start enjoying all this today!* All information should be verified by selling agent * Start enjoying all this today!
